author: Minecraft
description:
Oooooooh, who lives in a pineapple in Minecraft? SPONGEBOB SQUAREPANTS! That’s right, everyone’s favorite sponge is back in the SpongeBob SquarePants Biomes. Explore 18 new Bikini Bottom biomes, like Rock Bottom, Jellyfish Fields, Davey Jones’s Locker with SpongeBob, Squidward and all your pals. But before you can say, “I’m ready!”, make sure to stop by the Marketplace to grab your free Fishhook Hat.

Read more: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/spongebob-squarepants-biomes
title: Minecraft x SpongeBob SquarePants Biomes DLC
